  CNA National Warranty Corp | Products                                                Header Content                                             Product Landing Main Banner              PRODUCTS WE OFFER AND ADMINISTER Superior products that offer a variety of options for differing budgets and needs. Unparalleled service, transparent programs and long-term security backed by more than $55 billion in assets by CNA, one of the nation’s oldest insurance organizations.                 Product Landing Items                     Vehicle Service Contracts Vehicle service contracts were our first product, and they remain the focus of our operation today. A mechanical breakdown is never a pleasant experience so we have designed our claims process to ensure prompt and efficient support. Providing superior service includes working with the repair facility to quickly review the claim and provide coverage to get our customers back on the road.   Multiple coverage, terms and deductible options Rental car reimbursement Towing and emergency roadside assistance Thousands of repair locations to chose from No exclusions for pre-existing conditions, except for conditions that render the vehicle ineligible     VIEW PRODUCT DETAIL            Guaranteed Asset Protection (GAP) While you can't predict a theft or total loss, if it occurs, a Guaranteed Asset Protection (GAP) Waiver can help protect your wallet. As an optional addendum to your loan and designed to help cover the difference between the vehicle's actual cash value and the outstanding loan balance after a total loss, having a GAP Waiver can reduce or eliminate those out-of-pocket expenses.  For new and used vehicles Available for lease and loan financing agreements Finance for up to 84 months Finance up to 150 percent of MSRP (new vehicles) or NADA retail value (used vehicles) Multiple programs to choose from    VIEW PRODUCT DETAIL            Tire & Wheel You may not be able to avoid every bump in the road, but you can help eliminate the possible expense of repairing tire and wheel damage. When you encounter a road hazard that damages a tire or wheel, our Preferred Tire CareSM program covers the costs to repair the damaged tire or wheel and will even cover replacement when your tire no longer holds air and repairs are not possible.  Available for new and used vehicles Multiple term options No dollar limit per claim Transferable No deductible    VIEW PRODUCT DETAIL            Certified Warranty Select dealers offer Pro Certified Limited Warranties which are administered by CNA National. These warranties can help provide peace of mind against the unknowns that accompany the purchase of a used car. CNA National offers vehicle service contracts that "wrap" around the limited warranty coverage, adding additional years and often additional types of coverage, which can further help guard against unexpected repair costs. Ask your dealer today if they work with us so you can feel confident that you made the best choice during your used vehicle purchase. Contact our team today if you are a dealership interested in more information about the certified warranty program administered by CNA National.   VIEW PRODUCT DETAIL            Lifetime Limited Powertrain Warranty & Wrap The Lifetime Limited Powertrain Warranty, which we administer for select dealers, provides coverage for the major component groups of the powertrain for as long as you own the vehicle. Designed specifically to complement the Lifetime Limited Powertrain Warranty, CNA National offers vehicle service contracts that "wrap" around the warranty and expand and provide for additional parts coverage and benefits.   The Lifetime Limited Powertrain Warranty provides coverage for the engine, transmission and drivetrain The "wraps" are designed with exclusionary coverage for additional components and parts that expand and enhance the warranty Available for new and used vehicles at select dealerships Choice of wrap terms, including lifetime, to best suit the customer's needs    VIEW PRODUCT DETAIL                  Product Landing Awards           QUALITY PROVIDER & DISTINCTIVE PRODUCTS                An endorsed affinity partner of the American International Automobile Dealers Association (AIADA) since 1995                Best service contract provider for 13 years                Finalist in the BBB Business Ethics Awards for Arizona in 2015                             Footer Content                            

